OL,3,CPope Francis had another 'peaceful
OL,4,Cnight', says Vatican
OL,6,FPope Francis had another "peaceful
OL,7,Fnight", according to a brief update
OL,8,Ffrom the Vatican on Wednesday.
OL,10,FThere was no further update on the 88-
OL,11,Fyear-old pontiff's condition, which
OL,12,Fhas been described as "critical" as he
OL,13,Fbattles a lung infection that has
OL,14,Fsparked the early stages of kidney
OL,15,Finsufficiency.
OL,17,FThe Vatican said on Tuesday that Pope
OL,18,FFrancis had resumed work and was
OL,19,Feating normally , while doctors
OL,20,Fmonitored him at Rome's Gemelli
OL,21,Fhospital.
