OL,3,CPope Francis had another 'peaceful
OL,4,Cnight', says Vatican
OL,6,F"The Holy Father's clinical condition
OL,7,Fremains critical, but stationary... No
OL,8,Facute respiratory episodes occurred
OL,9,Fand hemodynamic parameters continue to
OL,10,Fbe stable," The Vatican said.
OL,12,F"In the evening he carried out a
OL,13,Fscheduled control CT scan for
OL,14,Fradiological monitoring of bilateral
OL,15,Fpneumonia... The prognosis remains
OL,16,Freserved.
OL,18,F"In the morning, after receiving the
OL,19,FEucharist, he resumed work."
