OL,3,CPope Francis had another 'peaceful
OL,4,Cnight', says Vatican
OL,6,FDoctors said on late Sunday he was in
OL,7,Fcritical condition but he hadn't
OL,8,Fexperienced any further respiratory
OL,9,Fcrises since Saturday.
OL,11,FFrancis was receiving high flows of
OL,12,Fsupplemental oxygen and, on Sunday,
OL,13,Fwas alert, and responsive, and even
OL,14,Fattended mass in the hospital chapel
OL,15,Fon Sunday with those caring for him.
OL,17,FDoctors described Francis' condition
OL,18,Fas touch-and-go, given his age,
OL,19,Ffragility and pre-existing lung
OL,20,Fdisease. He had part of one lung
OL,21,Fremoved as a young man.
