OL,3,CPope Francis had another 'peaceful
OL,4,Cnight', says Vatican
OL,6,F"In recent days, I have received many
OL,7,Fmessages of affection, and I have been
OL,8,Fparticularly struck by the letters and
OL,9,Fdrawings from children," he said in a
OL,10,Fstatement.
OL,12,F"Thank you for this closeness, and for
OL,13,Fthe prayers of comfort I have received
OL,14,Ffrom all over the world! I entrust you
OL,15,Fall to the intercession of Mary, and I
OL,16,Fask you to pray for me."
OL,18,FThis is his fourth hospitalisation
OL,19,Fsince his 2013 election, raising
OL,20,Fconcerns about his increasingly
OL,21,Ffragile health.
