OL,6,FAiling health
OL,8,FFrancis has other health problems as
OL,9,Fwell. He uses a wheelchair, walker, or
OL,10,Fcane to move around his apartment and
OL,11,Frecently fell twice, injuring his arm
OL,12,Fand chin.
OL,14,FIn 2021, he had 33cm of his large
OL,15,Fintestine removed due to a narrowing
OL,16,Fof the colon. Two years later, he
OL,17,Funderwent further abdominal surgery to
OL,18,Fremove scar tissue and repair a hernia.
