OL,6,FDuring a 2023 hospital stay, he was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with what he later described
OL,8,Fas "acute and strong pneumonia in the
OL,9,Flower part of the lungs".
OL,11,FBronchitis can sometimes develop into
OL,12,Fpneumonia, a more severe infection
OL,13,Faffecting the lungs' air sacs.
